## Project

### Name & Category
- **Project**: Soundness Gaming Arena
- **Category**: gaming

### Description
A decentralized gaming platform where players can join quick mini-games, earn points, and trade in-game assets. Scores and leaderboards are stored on-chain for transparency and fairness.

### SL Integration  
This project will use Soundness Layer for:

Fast and secure transaction processing for in-game actions

zkApp integration to verify fair play and prevent cheating

On-chain storage of player scores and assets

## Technical

### Architecture
A simple client-server structure:

Frontend communicates directly with Soundness Layer smart contracts

Game logic handled off-chain but results verified via zkProofs

Leaderboard and assets stored on-chain

### Stack
- **Frontend**: React.js / Next.js
- **Backend**: Node.js (optional for APIs)
- **Blockchain**: Soundness Layer testnet
- **Storage**: WALRUS/IPFS for game metadata

### Features
1. Wallet-based login


2. On-chain leaderboard


3. Asset minting & trading (simple NFTs as in-game items)

## Timeline

### PoC (2-4 weeks)
[x] Basic functionality (wallet connect, play game)

[x] SL integration for score submission

[ ] Simple UI

### MVP (4-8 weeks)  
[ ] Full feature set (leaderboard, asset trading)

[ ] Production-ready demo

[ ] User testing with community

## Innovation
Unlike traditional games, this project ensures transparency and fairness by putting scores and rewards on-chain. zkProof integration guarantees no cheating while keeping gameplay smooth.

